Class mp_RandomVariable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.software.reuze.mp_RandomVariable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    mp_i_Proposition, mp_i_PropositionTerm, mp_i_RandomVariable

    public class mp_RandomVariable
extends Object
implements mp_i_RandomVariable, mp_i_PropositionTerm
    Default implementation of the RandomVariable interface. Note: Also implements the TermProposition interface so its easy to use RandomVariables in conjunction with propositions about them in the Probability Model APIs.
    Author:
    Ciaran O'Reilly
